OL,5,G1800 Home and Away
OL,6,     FSonny pushes beyond his limits.
OL,7,     FLeah fights for Alf's reputation.
OL,8,     FDavid struggles with small-town
OL,9,     Fpolicing.
OL,10,G1830 New: Home and Away
OL,11,     FSonny refuses to play by the
OL,12,     Frules. Cash's turnaround is
OL,13,     Fshort-lived. Justin catches a
OL,14,     Flucky break.
OL,15,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,16,     FThis week the staff at the Hall
OL,17,     FGreen Health Centre in Birmingham
OL,18,     Fare getting ready for another busy
OL,19,     Fweek.
