OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FDocumentary series filmed inside
OL,7,     FBarnsley casualty department. A
OL,8,     Fbusy Monday becomes a
OL,9,     Frecord-breaker as the team deal
OL,10,     Fwith 349 patients.
OL,11,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,12,     FAn air ambulance is sent to help a
OL,13,     Ftree surgeon impaled on metal
OL,14,     Frailings; a 6-year-old is rushed
OL,15,     Fto hospital for head injuries; a
OL,16,     Fdouble amputee is found lying in a
OL,17,     Fpool of blood.
