OL,5,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FAn aggressive patient is
OL,7,     Frestrained in Newham as Dr Nick
OL,8,     Forders ketamine sedation for a
OL,9,     Fhead injury. In Belfast, teenager
OL,10,     FJack suffers spinal shock after a
OL,11,     Fhorrific motorcycle crash.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FFour top dermatologists treat
OL,14,     Fpatients for skin conditions such
OL,15,     Fas cysts, lipomas and skin tags
OL,16,     Fthat the NHS views as cosmetic,
OL,17,     Fbut that can hugely affect the
OL,18,     Fsufferers.
